00:13:41.460 --> 00:13:42.180
has sido tú.

00:13:44.620 --> 00:13:45.890
No finjas en un futuro

00:13:47.100 --> 00:13:47.700
delante de mí.

00:13:49.770 --> 00:13:51.050
No te preocupes, no te golpearé.

00:13:53.100 --> 00:13:53.740
Zorra.

00:13:55.310 --> 00:13:56.300
El cielo te castigará.

00:14:32.800 --> 00:14:33.810
Tú sí que estás libre.

00:14:38.760 --> 00:14:40.050
